metadata.name: ЯAЯE #1
metadata.description:
EDITION OF 10

Title: ЯAЯE  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2022

ЯAЯE by Godwits is a multi-edition art collection that dives into modern-day digital art with styles of printmaking and oil painting on a digital canvas. The artist uses software to create works that present traditional techniques and blend them with the current NFT culture.  

Collectors who own 10 or more will receive 1 of the non-sale pieces from the “Tribute: Contemporary” properties which are limited.  

These works are not for sale by the artist. These works will be airdropped to selected communities related to the content of the art. After the airdrop, The owners of the artwork are free to do as they please. The only way to obtain a ЯAЯE work is through the secondary market like OpenSea: https://opensea.io/collection/rare-by-godwits
